        </li>
        <li class="text-[#374151] text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          Set your name preference — <strong class="text-dark-heading font-semibold">default, short name, no numbers, or short with no numbers</strong>
        </li>
        <li class="text-[#374151] text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          Add an optional word in the Include field to personalize your results
        </li>
        <li class="text-[#374151] text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          Click Generate to get your Xbox gamertag ideas
        </li>
        <li class="text-[#374151] text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          Pick your favorite name from the results
